    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really nice shape and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. The engine runs smoothly, the interior is nice and tidy, and it\u2019s definitely ready to hit the road with a new owner! If you're looking for a reliable car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more miles, come check it out. I'm happy to answer any questions you have!",
