    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing for a precise, linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. This specimen utilizes a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring maximum engagement and traction. Critical enthusiast maintenance has been performed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, securing the structural and internal integrity of the platform. The chassis retains its sharp handling characteristics via a balanced MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension setup, complemented by staggered alloy wheels and ventilated rotors for consistent thermal management during spirited driving. A focused, high-performance machine ready for the open road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
